data.QUESTION: Why does Wang Qiang appear to be happy?
data.OPTION-A: Because he likes to listen to jokes
data.OPTION-B: Because he feels disappointed about the joke
data.OPTION-C: In order not to let other children think he is stupid
data.OPTION-D: Because he tells a better joke
